--------------
None


13. Multi-wavelength interface
------------------------------
None


14. Fermi-LAT interface
----------------------
None


15. CTA interface
-----------------
Added a simple offset angle dependence to the CTA response. The effective
area is assumed to vary following exp(-0.5*theta^4/sigma^2), where theta
is the offset angle of the photon arrival direction in the camera system
and sigma is a parameter that is set by default to 3.0 deg^2. No energy
dependence has been assumed in the offset angle variation.

Add NaN/Inf check to various classes.
